Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:08.05,Default,Recording,0,0,0,,You have one new message.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:09.93,Default,Voicemail,0,0,0,,This is your realtor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.93,0:00:13.32,Default,Voicemail,0,0,0,,Your electronic payment for\N last month's rent has not come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.61,0:00:17.50,Default,Voicemail,0,0,0,,Please make your payment to our account \Nby the end of the week at the very latest.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:23.23,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Business_Card,Biz card,0,0,0,,Hakamada Yukio \NAttorney at Law
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.61,0:00:33.71,Bengoshi-Tokiwa_Publishers,Label on building,0,0,0,,Tokiwa Publishers
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.38,0:00:33.49,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Kanae-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.71,0:00:37.08,Bengoshi-Credits_Kanae,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Hakamada's assistant \NNonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.10,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,It's your serial's one-year anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.10,0:00:36.30,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:37.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.83,0:00:40.36,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Plus, look at this reader \Nsurvey from last month.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:41.56,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,You're in third place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.39,Bengoshi-Reader_Survey,Survey top boldface words,0,0,0,,Monthly Manday March Issue: \N Author Popularity Rankings Based on Reader Survey {D: though it most likely is a play on the famous Shukan Sunday, they spell (probably incorrectly) as "Manday" so that's that; I had no way of knowing this until this episode} {We used Manday in the final for Ep 1, so sticking with that, sans the dash since he actually holds up a copy of the magazine, whoops. -E}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.48,0:00:43.39,Bengoshi-3rd_Place,Survey third from top,0,0,0,,3rd place: "{\c&H4E5E5F&}Divorce Chaser{\c}" Nonomura Kanae
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.65,0:00:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.66,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,This is the third consecutive month \Nyou've been ranked third, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:46.62,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,You're a full-fledged, \Npopular manga illustrator
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.62,0:00:48.25,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,and contributor to \NMonthly Manday, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.25,0:00:49.53,Default,Misato,0,0,0,,Nonomura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.53,0:00:51.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, don't call me that, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.90,0:00:55.27,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Chief editor of Tokiwa Publishers \NUeki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.19,0:00:54.53,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Nonomura-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:58.37,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,Would you be interested in doing a serial \Nfor the weekly publication of Manday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:00.31,Default,K,0,0,0,,Weekly Manday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.31,0:01:01.31,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,As you already know,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:03.77,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,it's Tokiwa Publishers' \Npowerhouse manga magazine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.77,0:01:06.62,Default,Ueki,0,0,0,,We publish {\i1}five times{\i0} the number of \Nissues of the monthly publication.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:09.96,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,Your monthly serial is highly \Nregarded by our readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.96,0:01:12.42,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,You can now move up as a \Nprofessional manga illustrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.42,0:01:15.79,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Editor at Tokiwa Publishing \NTabata Misato
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.61,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,Of course you'd have to end the \Ncurrent serial, which is too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.80,0:01:16.78,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,In the final episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:19.06,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,we want you to reveal \Nthe protagonist's past,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.09,0:01:19.22,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble,Manga bubble,0,0,0,,You will be divorcing\N your husband, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.06,0:01:20.79,Default,Tabata,0,0,0,,and bring the series to a \Nsupreme and conclusive end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.76,0:01:23.57,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You got a serial in Weekly Manday?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.74,0:01:24.65,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.65,0:01:27.27,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You've joined the ranks of top \Nmanga illustrators, Nonomura-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.27,0:01:28.71,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The pay! How much do you make?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.71,0:01:30.38,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is that an appropriate question?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.38,0:01:31.33,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You're so lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.33,0:01:32.86,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,You'll be super rich now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.70,0:01:35.10,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Freelance Investigator \NUmemoto Kurumi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.86,0:01:36.10,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Plus, you get monthly compensation\N from your ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.10,0:01:39.91,Default,K,0,0,0,,About that, he hasn't been depositing \Nthe compensation fee lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:40.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:41.27,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:42.94,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,That's quite common.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.65,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Temp \NShinozuka Rina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.94,0:01:44.36,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,When compensation gets divided \Ninto monthly payments,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:46.23,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,those men eventually fade out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:48.68,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,But even if you grow in \Npopularity, even if you get rich,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.68,0:01:50.26,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,you have to make him keep paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.26,0:01:51.32,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.32,0:01:54.16,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You can never get enough income.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:56.39,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Office landlord \NToyama Yoshie
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.16,0:01:57.11,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I'll teach you how to rent out apartments!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:02:00.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, to tell you the truth, \NI'm still hesitant.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.55,Default,K,0,0,0,,If I have to do a weekly serial,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.55,0:02:05.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'd be too busy to continue\N working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.80,0:02:06.73,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.73,0:02:08.17,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Why are you hesitating about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.17,0:02:09.05,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:11.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You should dump this place. \NThe faster, the better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.45,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,We don't get paid consistently, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.68,0:02:16.80,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.28,0:02:21.22,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Attorney \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:21.95,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,Anyway, let's celebrate\NKanae-chan's promotion today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:23.27,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Sensei, pour some sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:27.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait...\NYoshie-san, not so fast, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.22,0:02:30.05,Default,K,0,0,0,,I haven't received \NHakamada-sensei's permission, yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:31.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,You have my complete approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:34.91,Default,H,0,0,0,,You were once my client,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:38.13,Default,H,0,0,0,,but you carved out a path for yourself, \Nand are about to begin a new life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:40.50,Default,H,0,0,0,,What better news can there be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.11,0:02:42.77,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Come on, Kanae-chan. Drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.41,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei, my glass is empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:02:54.44,Default,H,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.04,Default,K,0,0,0,,Hurry up. Sensei, why aren't \Nyou drinking, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:02:59.32,Default,H,0,0,0,,I can't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.32,0:03:01.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're seriously a bore of \Na man, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:03.75,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sensei, how come you never got married?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:11.29,Default,K,0,0,0,,If you're not drinking, at least \Nentertain me with stories or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.37,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kanae-chan, maybe you shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:16.61,Default,H,0,0,0,,Well, I've never felt the \Nneed to get married...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:19.24,Default,K,0,0,0,,Be honest. Tell the truth, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.42,0:03:20.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,Keep it coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.05,0:03:24.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,Wait, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:25.99,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're gay? Gay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.24,0:03:26.21,Bengoshi-Overlap,H,0,0,0,,No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:28.26,Default,K,0,0,0,,I knew it! He's gay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.67,0:03:32.03,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,If they're busy, I can come back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.62,0:03:35.00,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Oh... one moment please.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:38.19,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Kanae's ex-husband \NKurasawa Yoshihito
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.91,0:03:38.19,Default,Voices,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.19,0:03:42.46,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You know, it's because he's seen \Nso many failures come through his office.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.46,0:03:43.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,"Failures"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:45.51,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:47.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,Were you talking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.30,0:03:49.22,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, I didn't say anything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:52.02,Default,K,0,0,0,,Sure, my marriage was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:56.27,Default,K,0,0,0,,But I chalked it up to experience, \Nyou understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.27,0:04:00.95,Default,K,0,0,0,,How could I have known that \Nhusband was an adulterer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:03.00,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei, please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:03.82,Default,H,0,0,0,,Oh, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.65,0:04:07.19,Default,K,0,0,0,,You can't escape me, Hakamada!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.07,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,We have a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.07,0:04:10.92,Default,K,0,0,0,,A client?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.65,Default,K,0,0,0,,Y-Yoshihito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.14,0:04:16.16,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:17.53,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:19.40,Default,K,0,0,0,,Oh, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.88,0:04:22.90,Default,K,0,0,0,,I work here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.47,0:04:27.73,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Sorry I've been late on \Ncompensation payments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.81,0:04:33.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,You came here to tell me that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.65,0:04:37.45,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Actually, I came to consult \NHakamada-sensei today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.17,0:04:40.12,Default,H,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:50.72,Bengoshi-Title,,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser\N {\fs25}~Let's Turn Your Tears into Money~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:55.90,Bengoshi-Ep_Title,Caption left,0,0,0,,Divorce Chaser Episode 11\N An unsurmountable crisis!! \NA formidable attorney enters the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.46,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.74,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I apologize for having caused\N you trouble in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.74,0:05:01.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.95,0:05:05.15,Default,H,0,0,0,,So, what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.56,0:05:07.59,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.94,0:05:10.72,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,it's about another \Ncompensation lawsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.48,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Compensation?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.88,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That guy never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.88,0:05:15.04,Default,Y,0,0,0,,He must've cheated again.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.32,0:05:17.78,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,He's sick, that's all. Sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.78,0:05:19.93,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,He's truly divorce material.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.17,0:05:21.34,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Right, Kanae-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.06,0:05:26.08,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.82,0:05:29.46,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,It wasn't me who was cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.90,0:05:31.25,Default,Y,0,0,0,,You heard us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:32.52,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.50,0:05:35.98,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,The one caught cheating was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.20,0:05:39.58,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,my wife, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.76,0:05:42.30,Default,K,0,0,0,,Shiori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:47.31,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,0)}Yoshihito's wife \NKurasawa Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.22,0:05:45.33,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.78,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Soon after my divorce with Kanae was official,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:49.98,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,we legalized our union.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.52,0:05:52.61,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,But I had a monthly \Ncompensation fee to pay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.85,0:05:55.97,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,and couldn't afford to give her \Nthe kind of life she expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.25,0:05:58.37,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,Do you like this? Isn't it cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:05:59.84,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,How much was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:02.25,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,It was on sale. It wasn't much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:03.21,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,About 50,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.90,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you we don't have \Nthat kind of money right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:11.47,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,Oh. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.75,0:06:15.59,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Eventually cracks started \Nshowing in our marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.59,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.82,Bengoshi-Text_Dinner,Text,0,0,0,,I'm going to a dinner party with friends tonight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:38.86,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,And then, I received an envelope \Nwith a letter from a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.37,0:06:46.20,Bengoshi-Compensation_Paper,Letter top,0,0,0,,Compensation lawsuit for damages\N incurred from illicit activities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.89,0:06:47.24,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori was accused of \Nillicit activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.67,Bengoshi-Illicit_Activities,Letter zoom,0,0,0,,illicit activities
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.24,0:06:51.24,Bengoshi-Illicit_Activities,Zoom,0,0,0,,3 million yen in damages
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.35,0:06:50.95,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Three million yen in compensation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.95,0:06:51.70,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.02,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,My wife's illicit partner had a wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.63,0:06:59.12,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,It was the wife who filed \Nthe lawsuit against Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.62,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Is that what you call \Na double-adultery?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.06,0:07:03.24,Default,Kur,0,0,0,,Your wife never learns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:06.78,Default,Rita,0,0,0,,She's the kind who wants \Nwhat she can't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:10.06,Default,H,0,0,0,,Has Shiori-san admitted \Nto illicit activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:11.83,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:13.38,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:15.22,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.13,0:07:18.84,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.63,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,It's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:27.81,Bengoshi-Flashback,Shiori,0,0,0,,Our married life wasn't what \Nyou promised it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.34,Bengoshi-Flashback,Yosh,0,0,0,,Shiori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.35,0:07:33.31,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,My wife moved in with \Nher parents after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:35.29,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,We're living separately now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.01,0:07:36.90,Default,H,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:40.15,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,We have no savings,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.42,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,or any means of paying \Nfor compensation, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.75,0:07:48.23,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you \Ncould help me somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.59,Default,H,0,0,0,,Are you sure you \Nwant {\i1}me{\i0} to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:54.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the one
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.83,Default,H,0,0,0,,who slapped you with an \Nexorbitant lawsuit in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.24,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Actually, it was because of that, \Nthat I am now seeking your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:08.93,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,We're scheduled for a talk with the \Nother party's legal representative soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:14.12,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I was hoping you could \Nsit in on the session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:24.80,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign,Words,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:25.90,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Today's the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:27.00,Default,K,0,0,0,,Of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.35,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You know, the meeting with your ex-husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.68,0:08:31.91,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,The other lawyer's \Ncoming here today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.91,0:08:33.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.75,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Kanae-san, are you okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.13,Default,K,0,0,0,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:43.67,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei is going to represent \Nyour ex-husband's obnoxious wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:47.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,That's Hakamada-sensei's \Ndecision to make, not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:55.38,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.30,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You don't have to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:03.54,Default,H,0,0,0,,Good to have you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:04.83,Default,H,0,0,0,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.16,0:09:06.70,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.04,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,{\i1}This{\i0} is your lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:09.69,Default,H,0,0,0,,It has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.07,0:09:11.41,Default,H,0,0,0,,I'm Hakamada, attorney at law.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.91,0:09:13.38,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Wait a second, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.22,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Why's it have to be this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.02,0:09:16.84,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:25.55,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,And what's your ex-wife doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:28.70,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Well... she's been working here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.79,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,You've been seeing your ex, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.79,0:09:32.65,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,And you have the nerve\N to berate me for cheating.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.65,0:09:34.77,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,That's not how it is, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:38.73,Default,H,0,0,0,,Before we have our discussion \Nwith the other party's attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:41.46,Default,H,0,0,0,,I have a few questions for Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.05,0:09:43.72,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I have nothing to say to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:44.47,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.43,0:09:49.18,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Our married life was ruined \Nbecause of this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:51.80,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Can't we find another lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.03,0:09:54.61,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei is \Nan outstanding lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:56.86,Default,Yoshi,0,0,0,,He's on our side now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:00.23,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Your ex-wife is working \Nat this office, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.76,0:10:03.92,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,She might sabotage us out of revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.95,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, that kind of thing will not happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.32,0:10:08.90,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Anyway, I refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.39,0:10:13.96,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I'd rather pay the lawsuit \Nand get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:18.15,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I want a fresh start,\N as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.88,0:10:31.11,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.11,0:10:32.34,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Oh, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.55,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I am Honjo Yayoi-san's \Nlegal representative,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:36.09,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Karasuma Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.63,0:10:41.87,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Hakamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:45.74,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it, Hakamada-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.70,0:10:48.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,It has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.33,0:10:53.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Even when I heard "Hakamada Law Office,"\N I never expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.33,0:10:56.27,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,But, you're still practicing law.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.87,0:10:58.33,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:10:59.61,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.29,0:11:01.11,Default,H,0,0,0,,Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.49,Bengoshi-Credits_Left,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Sieg Law Office attorney \NKarasuma Keiko
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:05.48,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,We worked at the same law firm\N before I went solo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.86,0:11:08.18,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You were very kind to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.91,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You were a corporate lawyer, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.55,0:11:13.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.48,0:11:16.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,In fact, I still specialize\N in corporate law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:20.03,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I'm the in-house attorney\N for Honjo Industries
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.18,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,presided over by my client, \NHonjo Takashi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.37,0:11:25.85,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,who has requested that \NI represent his wife in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.85,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I look forward to working with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.31,0:11:35.72,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Outside_Sign,Sign,0,0,0,,Hakamada \NLaw Office
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.12,0:11:35.71,Default,H,0,0,0,,Will your client be joining us today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.92,0:11:40.73,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,suffered a physical breakdown after she \Ndiscovered her husband's affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.03,0:11:42.49,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,She will not be joining us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:43.90,Default,H,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:45.28,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Kanae-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.10,0:11:47.66,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You're curious, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:49.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.61,0:11:51.88,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm going to go hunt for material.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.88,0:11:54.28,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Well then, to begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:55.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,please have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.90,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,These are only a part of \Nthe evidence of the illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.38,0:12:05.28,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You have been seeing him with \Nsome frequency, documented here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.28,0:12:06.81,Bengoshi-Compensation_Paper,Letter top,0,0,0,,{\a4\3c&H90898F&}Adultery investigation report
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:08.02,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,So many times...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,Can everything listed here be proven?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.24,0:12:12.86,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.34,0:12:14.75,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Care to have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:18.59,Default,H,0,0,0,,I will study it later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:20.63,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Based on our evidence,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:25.13,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,we are suing Shiori-san \Nfor five million yen in compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.63,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Five million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.63,0:12:29.30,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Isn't that higher than the figure \Nyou gave me the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:34.82,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san and Takashi-san are getting \Na divorce due to his illicit affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:36.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,As a result,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.29,0:12:39.13,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san has suffered \Npsychological illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:42.25,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Hence, this trauma was added\N in the compensation fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:43.18,Default,H,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.51,0:12:46.99,Default,H,0,0,0,,Is there a causal connection between \Nthe illicit affair and mental illness?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Shiori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:52.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,When did you start seeing Takashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.56,0:12:55.22,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.46,0:12:58.79,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,According to Takashi-san, \Nit started six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:03.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yayoi-san discovered \Nit four months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:08.47,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This is the doctor's diagnosis report.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:12.34,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,The time coincides with her \Nbeing diagnosed with depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:12.71,Bengoshi-Diagnosis,Diagnosis report top,0,0,0,,{\b1}Diagnosis {\b0}\NMrs. Honjo Yayoi \N{\b1}Ailment:{\b0} Depression \NThe above named upon examination has been diagnosed with severe and self-harming depression. We suggest protective hospitalization for one month to monitor her condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.85,0:13:16.66,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There is no question that\N the situation impacted Yayoi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:19.59,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Why am I being blamed for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:21.93,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Takashi-san came onto me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:25.08,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Actually, not according to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:32.20,Bengoshi-Text_Shiori,Text snapshot top,0,0,0,,Shiori
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:32.20,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side,First text (white bubble),0,0,0,,Takashi-san r u free next week??
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.52,0:13:32.20,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side,Green bubble,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.39,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,This side is Shiori-san's texts,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:29.74,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,the other is Takashi-san's.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:32.20,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side,Second white bubble,0,0,0,,{\a6}I want us to go to Yokohama next time <3 \NThere's a super yummy pancake place there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.42,0:13:33.74,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It is clear from this that Shiori-san \Nwas the active initiator.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.43,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side,Second green bubble,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.43,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side,Third white bubble,0,0,0,,Take me out for lunch today
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:35.43,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side,Third green bubble,0,0,0,,{\a3}Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.44,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Those aren't real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:40.12,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,You can fabricate texts.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.89,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Fabrications, you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:46.35,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Shiori-san, may I see your cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:49.81,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Perhaps the same conversation\N is in the history.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:58.19,Bengoshi-Shiori_Text_Side2,First text (white bubble),0,0,0,,Takashi-san r u free next week??  \N\NI want us to go to Yokohama next time <3  \NThere's a super yummy pancake place there. \N  \NTake me out for lunch today {D: heart-eyes smiley emoji}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.55,0:13:58.19,Bengoshi-Takashi_Text_Side2,Green bubble,0,0,0,,Yes.  \N \NUnderstood.  \N \NUnderstood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.68,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:04.62,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I forgot because we always \Ntalked on the phone instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:07.59,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Then prove to us that you have \Nhad those phone conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:10.11,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Prove? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.22,0:14:13.80,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Do you have any recorded conversations?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.17,0:14:16.11,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Who records phone conversations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.46,0:14:18.28,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,I understand the case you are making.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.79,0:14:24.08,Default,H,0,0,0,,We will examine the material,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.79,Default,H,0,0,0,,and respond to you accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.87,0:14:30.36,Default,H,0,0,0,,However, five million yen
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:33.20,Default,H,0,0,0,,is beyond Shiori-san's means.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.26,0:14:37.09,Default,H,0,0,0,,I believe you would \Nhave to reconsider it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.83,0:14:41.96,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You're not just trying to\N buy time, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.83,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.52,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.22,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:56.76,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,That compensation fee...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.72,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Am I the only one liable for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.81,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Fundamentally, that would be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:03.22,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:08.58,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,where you get the money \Nis not our concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.04,0:15:12.24,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.40,0:15:21.70,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Hey, can I be sure this \NSensei is trustworthy?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.22,0:15:24.52,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,He didn't even argue in my favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.52,0:15:27.93,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Well, that was a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.59,0:15:33.77,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I apologize for her rudeness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:38.85,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Do you think we stand \Nany kind of chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.38,0:15:40.87,Default,H,0,0,0,,To be frank,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.75,Default,H,0,0,0,,we are at a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.18,0:15:49.03,Default,H,0,0,0,,You might have to brace yourselves\N to pay the compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:51.32,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.10,0:15:54.16,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:10.18,Bengoshi-Honjo_Sign,Plaque,0,0,0,,Honjo
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.30,0:16:13.91,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I had a conference with the other \Nparty's legal representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:15.69,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Takashi's wife \NHonjo Yayoi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.63,0:16:16.19,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.95,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,And how did that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.98,0:16:19.51,Bengoshi-Overlap,Takashi,0,0,0,,You can leave now,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:21.00,Bengoshi-Overlap,Takashi,0,0,0,,I'll hear what she's got to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.23,0:16:23.75,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,But {\i1}I'm{\i0} her client—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:25.92,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Never mind. You don't need to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.23,Bengoshi-Credits_Ueki,Caption,0,0,0,,Shiori's illicit partner \NHonjo Takashi
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.41,0:16:29.60,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:34.10,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.32,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,What did they say about the \Nincreased compensation fee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.30,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There is no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:43.15,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,The other party made only one statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.55,0:16:46.72,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That it would be difficult \Nto make the payment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:48.63,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.09,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,But it was merely\N an appeal to sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:54.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There are many ways to extract \Ncompensation from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.02,0:16:57.09,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,I made the right decision \Nhiring you for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:16:59.25,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,And it's not even your specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.58,0:17:00.52,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,You're splendid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.63,0:17:01.95,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Speaking as an attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.25,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,divorce cases are the easiest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:07.40,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,If we are well prepared, \Nour victory is assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.66,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Your instill me with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.41,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,By the way, I hear you're \Nacquainted with the other lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.87,0:17:16.38,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.79,0:17:17.98,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Lucky me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:20.45,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,He is an easily-defeated opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.92,0:17:22.32,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:23.76,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:26.68,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,until the compensation \Nagreement is finalized,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:29.26,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,you must continue living \Ntogether with your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.16,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.17,0:17:32.36,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,Yayoi, did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:36.42,Default,Takashi,0,0,0,,It's only because you'll need \Nthe money after our divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:37.65,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.68,Default,Yayoi,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.28,0:17:43.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.55,0:17:44.64,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,We've got trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.64,0:17:46.45,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Sensei is baking good bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.45,0:17:47.08,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.42,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Try it for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:51.67,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,It's better than the highest quality \Nbread at the Imperial Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:58.22,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're right. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.31,0:18:00.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,Which can only mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.32,0:18:01.06,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.06,0:18:03.32,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,His anxiety this time is \Nalso of the highest quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.68,0:18:07.94,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.66,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Wait. Hold on, Shiori.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.13,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,They sent me this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.07,Bengoshi-Reader_Survey,Letter zoom,0,0,0,,{\fs23}{\3c&HC0B2A5&}Provisional seizure notice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:19.08,Default,H,0,0,0,,A provisional seizure notice...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:20.36,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.50,0:18:25.09,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,It's possible to seize the other \Nparty's assets even before a trial,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:30.52,Bengoshi-Vocab_Word,Caption orange,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Provisional seizure notice
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:30.52,Bengoshi-Vocab_Definition,Caption white,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)}Notice proclaiming seizure of properties and income before trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.76,0:18:28.20,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,by simply reporting the \Nillicit activities to a court.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:34.48,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,This implies Shiori-san's future \Nincome will be garnished.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.86,0:18:37.55,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Huh? They can take her income, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.74,0:18:42.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,They can garnish up \Nto 25% of her income.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.76,0:18:45.26,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I can't make a living \Nif they take that much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:48.03,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.76,0:18:53.00,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,There's a provisional seizure notice \Nof the bank account in Shiori's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.00,0:18:54.77,Default,H,0,0,0,,You had said you had no savings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.08,0:18:58.34,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,This was a fund we kept \Nfor our wedding ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.11,0:18:59.15,Bengoshi-Illicit_Activities,Notice,0,0,0,,{\c&H3D2F2C&\3c&HE1D1C8&}{\fs23}Authorization for seizure, index{\fs}\NAmount total: {\b1}2 million yen{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.68,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Because we haven't had one yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:04.16,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,I moved my savings to her account,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.48,0:19:06.44,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,and we've been adding to it since.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.32,0:19:10.35,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,Do I have to give it to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:11.27,Default,H,0,0,0,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.00,0:19:14.14,Default,H,0,0,0,,if the compensation lawsuit \Nbecomes officially recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.35,0:19:16.38,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,But, that's where you come in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.43,0:19:20.31,Default,H,0,0,0,,I don't know what to tell you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.03,0:19:24.96,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,I told you we should \Ngo to another lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.96,0:19:25.53,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.74,0:19:27.82,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,What's so good about this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.19,0:19:29.79,Default,Shiori,0,0,0,,They're beating the crap out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.47,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Come on. Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.36,Default,H,0,0,0,,No, Shiori-san is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.61,0:19:39.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,So for this particular case,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:42.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,I think you should consult \Na different lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:44.55,Default,Yosh,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.13,0:26:58.60,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.86,0:26:59.92,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.28,0:27:01.67,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where is Hakamada-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.94,0:27:04.88,Default,Y,0,0,0,,He got a call, and dashed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.56,0:27:06.59,Default,K,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.65,0:27:10.33,Default,Y,0,0,0,,How's the weekly manga serial going?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.57,0:27:11.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,Well, so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.63,0:27:14.32,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What was that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.32,0:27:16.25,Default,Y,0,0,0,,It seems you're not making \Nany progress with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.23,0:27:19.93,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Are you bothered by your \Nex-husband's situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.62,0:27:24.03,Default,Y,0,0,0,,It's not anything you need \Nto be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.70,0:27:27.48,Default,Y,0,0,0,,That husband's only \Nreaping what he's sown.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.48,0:27:29.58,Default,K,0,0,0,,It's not him I'm concerned for,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.58,0:27:31.16,Default,K,0,0,0,,it's Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:32.77,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:33.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.00,0:27:36.70,Default,K,0,0,0,,Something's not quite right \Nwith Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.70,0:27:38.53,Default,K,0,0,0,,Especially after he met\N the other's party's lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.95,0:27:39.86,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.14,0:27:41.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,Someone called Karasuma-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.85,0:27:43.45,Default,K,0,0,0,,from the Sieg Law Office.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.10,0:27:44.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.64,0:27:47.14,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Could that be Karasuma Keiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.44,0:27:48.25,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.69,0:27:50.06,Default,K,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.94,0:27:52.32,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Karasuma Keiko is...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.32,0:27:55.25,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei's ex-lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.93,0:27:56.61,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.84,0:27:57.97,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,Ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.19,0:28:03.54,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei was working at a \Nfirm specializing in corporate law.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.19,0:28:05.23,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Plaque,Plaque,0,0,0,,{\fs20}Attorney at law{\fs} \NHakamada Yukio
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.96,0:28:02.49,Bengoshi-Timestamp,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}10 years ago
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.92,0:28:06.64,Default,Y,0,0,0,,He was an outstanding new \Nlawyer, with a lot of promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.96,0:28:10.36,Default,Y,0,0,0,,He was in charge of forty \Nclients at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.36,0:28:11.26,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,Hakamada-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.86,0:28:14.20,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,the damages lawsuit of \NAsabishi Brokerage...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.60,0:28:19.98,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Karasuma Keiko was working \Non the same team at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.98,0:28:22.72,Default,Y,0,0,0,,They worked perfectly \N with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.72,0:28:24.91,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The two of them won every case \Nthey fought together as a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.17,0:28:26.48,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,Ready for the shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.76,0:28:27.91,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,Strike a pose...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.68,0:28:33.90,Default,Y,0,0,0,,They soon got closer and closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.46,0:28:36.40,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,That's enough pictures of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.40,0:28:38.43,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Let's ask someone to take\N a picture of us together.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.43,0:28:39.53,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.53,0:28:41.46,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,Okay, one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.07,0:28:47.34,Default,Y,0,0,0,,I think Hakamada-sensei was \Nplanning to get married to Keiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.52,0:28:50.53,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Please marry me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.16,0:28:52.15,Default,Y,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.33,0:29:12.88,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,What's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.92,0:29:18.43,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,That's a client who is negotiating with our firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.17,0:29:21.63,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,And that's not all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.23,0:29:28.52,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,How many relationships have you had?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.56,0:29:33.50,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Please tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.68,0:29:38.19,Bengoshi-Division_Manager,Plaque,0,0,0,,Division Manager's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.02,0:29:38.02,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.92,0:29:40.68,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Division Manager, you wanted to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.77,0:29:44.94,Bengoshi-Flashback,DM,0,0,0,,Karasuma-kun told me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.76,0:29:50.54,Bengoshi-Flashback,DM,0,0,0,,I'm disappointed in you, Hakamada-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.92,0:29:52.01,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.01,0:29:53.90,Bengoshi-Flashback,DM,0,0,0,,You're a professional attorney,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.37,0:29:56.76,Bengoshi-Flashback,DM,0,0,0,,and you're stalking your coworker?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.45,0:29:58.45,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Stalking?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.08,0:30:03.97,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,No, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.25,0:30:05.44,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,We've been seeing each other \Nfor six months now and—
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.44,0:30:07.08,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,That is false.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.69,0:30:10.45,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,It was all in Hakamada-san's own head.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.74,0:30:13.02,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.15,0:30:15.12,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,It's all this man's delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.83,0:30:18.03,Bengoshi-Flashback,Keiko,0,0,0,,There's no proof whatsoever \Nthat I've been seeing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.68,0:30:20.16,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,I do have proof of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.96,0:30:25.40,Default,Y,0,0,0,,And there was no photo, no email
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.64,0:30:27.20,Default,Y,0,0,0,,that would have proven \Ntheir relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.46,0:30:29.13,Default,Y,0,0,0,,They were all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.94,0:30:33.43,Default,Y,0,0,0,,It was as if she had \Nanticipated what was coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.52,0:30:37.49,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei was falsely \Naccused of stalking ten years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.94,0:30:39.72,Default,Y,0,0,0,,and was fired from the law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.61,0:30:49.33,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Karasuma Keiko took over \Nall of Hakamada-sensei cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.00,0:30:53.43,Default,Y,0,0,0,,She used Hakamada-sensei \Nas a stepping stone
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.85,0:30:58.01,Default,Y,0,0,0,,to get promoted at the law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.83,0:31:00.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,What did Hakamada-sensei do after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:04.33,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Bad rumors about him spread,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.19,0:31:09.27,Default,Y,0,0,0,,and he couldn't work in \Ncorporate law any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.92,0:31:12.58,Default,Y,0,0,0,,A little while later,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.04,0:31:15.77,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Hakamada-sensei opened this law office.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.56,0:31:18.37,Default,Y,0,0,0,,He wanted to save people
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.93,0:31:23.92,Default,Y,0,0,0,,from the same kind of pain he endured.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.80,0:31:30.73,Default,K,0,0,0,,So that's why he decided \Nto become a divorce lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.45,0:31:45.24,Default,H,0,0,0,,Karasuma-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.77,0:31:50.12,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I'm glad you accepted my \Ninvitation, Hakamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.81,0:31:55.97,Default,H,0,0,0,,What would you like to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.24,0:31:58.66,Default,H,0,0,0,,I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.30,0:32:00.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,A glass of water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.48,0:32:01.48,Default,Tenderbar,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.06,0:32:04.61,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I remember. You don't drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.90,0:32:07.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,I came here because you said
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.76,0:32:09.65,Default,H,0,0,0,,you had information \Nconcerning the current case.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.92,0:32:14.21,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested \Nin husband-wife squabbles.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.21,0:32:16.06,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,We all know who will win, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.46,0:32:17.74,Default,Tenderbar,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.90,0:32:18.83,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,On another note,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.89,0:32:21.62,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,would you be interested \Nin joining our firm?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.96,0:32:25.04,Default,H,0,0,0,,You have some nerve, asking me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.46,0:32:26.88,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Come on, Hakamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.88,0:32:29.99,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,You didn't become a lawyer \N  to handle divorce cases, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.34,0:32:33.06,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,It's a lot of tedious \Nwork with little payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.41,0:32:36.60,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Oh, and I did a background \Ncheck of your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.12,0:32:39.48,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,About two or three clients per month...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:42.83,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,After deducting all expenses, \Nyou must be flat broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.92,0:32:46.02,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,If you join our firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.47,0:32:48.24,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,you'll make ten times \Nwhat you're making now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.61,0:32:50.23,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,That is, judging by your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.57,0:32:55.48,Default,H,0,0,0,,I don't practice law for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.52,0:32:58.20,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,What do you do it for, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.94,0:33:02.20,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Oh, yes. I remember what you \Nsaid a long time ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.70,0:33:04.78,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,"The work of the attorney is \Nto walk in your clients' shoes,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.16,0:33:10.17,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,and discover the best \Nways to help them."
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.59,0:33:16.17,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,But can you say the same for \Nclients with malicious intent?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.36,0:33:20.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Lawyers can't choose their clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.93,0:33:25.37,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,We are obligated to protect even \Nthose we'd rather not protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:28.44,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Justice is a relative thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.76,0:33:34.44,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Therefore our sole concern \Nis whether we win or lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.23,0:33:39.29,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,There's no justice beyond that concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.29,0:33:45.46,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.30,0:33:49.67,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,still holding a grudge from that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.79,0:33:55.03,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I was desperate, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.41,0:33:57.83,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I wanted to further my career a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.89,0:33:59.72,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:02.50,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,When it came to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.50,0:34:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't like I got close to you \Njust to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.68,0:34:08.52,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,My feelings for you were genuine—
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.52,0:34:09.76,Default,H,0,0,0,,Let's not talk about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.01,0:34:13.84,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.88,0:34:16.81,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,drop by our office if you want a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.05,0:34:24.70,Default,H,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.90,0:34:25.96,Default,Tenderbar,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.85,0:34:28.57,Default,Tenderbar,0,0,0,,That lady who was with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.93,0:34:30.41,Default,Tenderbar,0,0,0,,She left without paying.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.14,0:34:36.54,Bengoshi-Hakamada_Window_Sign3,Words,0,0,0,,Hakamada Law Office
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.17,0:34:45.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Where were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.99,0:34:50.50,Default,H,0,0,0,,I should ask you. What are \Nyou doing here so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.81,0:34:53.64,Default,K,0,0,0,,Waiting for you, Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.70,0:34:55.52,Default,H,0,0,0,,Waiting for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.45,0:35:04.96,Default,K,0,0,0,,Please don't turn Yoshihito-san down.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.73,0:35:06.89,Default,H,0,0,0,,As I have already explained,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.32,0:35:08.57,Default,H,0,0,0,,he doesn't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.89,0:35:11.77,Default,K,0,0,0,,Is that because your opponent \Nis Karasuma Keiko-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.65,0:35:16.93,Default,K,0,0,0,,Yoshie-san told me about \Nyour past history with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.93,0:35:20.42,Default,Y,0,0,0,,She did it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.44,0:35:24.52,Default,K,0,0,0,,Are you going to compromise your \Nfortitude for something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.71,0:35:28.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,This isn't like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.43,0:35:31.20,Default,K,0,0,0,,You have always put yourself \Nin your clients' shoes, always!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.20,0:35:33.84,Default,K,0,0,0,,Then you'd always find the \Nbest ways to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.36,0:35:35.66,Default,K,0,0,0,,But not this time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.10,0:35:38.97,Default,K,0,0,0,,The opposing lawyer was your ex,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.97,0:35:39.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,so you're cowering and running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.98,0:35:41.74,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're just trying to \Nprotect yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.74,0:35:42.86,Default,H,0,0,0,,That is not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.86,0:35:44.37,Default,K,0,0,0,,Why did you refuse him, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.10,0:35:47.14,Default,K,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.14,0:35:48.86,Default,K,0,0,0,,Those aren't Hakamada-sensei's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.96,0:35:58.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,I read this month's issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.81,0:36:02.49,Default,H,0,0,0,,The protagonist's crisis \Nin the story is trite.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.90,0:36:03.56,Default,K,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.66,0:36:07.80,Default,H,0,0,0,,It makes me wonder if you can \Nhandle a weekly serial.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.73,0:36:10.12,Default,H,0,0,0,,Now, how did that feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.31,0:36:12.26,Default,H,0,0,0,,to hear an opinion from \Nan absolute amateur?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.45,0:36:15.33,Default,H,0,0,0,,You're doing the same thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.04,0:36:19.02,Default,H,0,0,0,,If you have time to be \Nconcerned about my work,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.54,0:36:22.01,Default,H,0,0,0,,you should be getting ready\N for your weekly serials instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.25,0:36:24.42,Default,H,0,0,0,,I don't want to hear the opinions
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.94,0:36:26.62,Default,H,0,0,0,,of someone getting ready to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.89,0:36:29.98,Default,K,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.58,0:36:32.72,Default,K,0,0,0,,But before I quit,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.96,0:36:35.49,Default,K,0,0,0,,I'm going to take over \Nthis case, and settle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.46,0:36:39.52,Default,H,0,0,0,,There's nothing \Nthat you could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.90,0:36:45.43,Default,K,0,0,0,,I have been watching you \Nwork for a whole year now.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.25,0:36:49.32,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know the methods you've \Nused to help your clients.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.32,0:36:50.85,Default,K,0,0,0,,I know them very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:55.82,Default,K,0,0,0,,So, I'm going to help that client,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.82,0:36:57.63,Default,K,0,0,0,,the way that you would do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.25,0:37:13.34,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Sorry to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.98,0:37:16.21,Default,Y,0,0,0,,but I agree with Kanae-chan's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.61,0:37:19.44,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The way you've been lately, \NHakamada-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.19,0:37:22.72,Default,Y,0,0,0,,is not like Hakamada-sensei at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.83,0:37:26.86,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Not only have you not put \Nyourself in your client's shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.23,0:37:30.78,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You don't even understand \NKanae-san's feelings, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.66,0:37:34.88,Default,H,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.48,0:37:38.95,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,Kanae-san turned down \Nthe weekly syndication.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.42,0:37:41.59,Default,H,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.17,0:37:45.78,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,She said she didn't want to discontinue \Nthe monthly Divorce Chaser manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.17,0:37:49.37,Default,Y,0,0,0,,To succeed as a manga illustrator,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.37,0:37:51.97,Default,Y,0,0,0,,weekly serials are the fastest track.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.38,0:37:54.22,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.03,0:37:59.74,Default,Y,0,0,0,,she said she wants share what \Nshe learns at this law office,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.74,0:38:01.75,Default,Y,0,0,0,,with all her readers.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.26,0:38:06.00,Default,Y,0,0,0,,She wants to help people, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.16,0:38:10.36,Default,Y,0,0,0,,using whatever means \Nshe has at her disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.14,0:38:15.60,Default,Y,0,0,0,,In the same way that you \Nhepled her, Hakamada-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.07,0:38:23.88,Default,Y,0,0,0,,Kanae-chan must be pulling out \Nher hair, seeing you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.61,0:38:47.88,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Compensation,Right bubble; last shot,0,0,0,,You will pay the\N compensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.15,0:38:47.88,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Left,Left bubble1,0,0,0,,Of all the men\N I have ever met ...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.15,0:38:47.88,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Left,Left bubble2,0,0,0,,{\a1\3c&H435456&}you are a "dumb man"\N of the highest order.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.79,0:38:54.16,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,And yet, notwithstanding, you haven't \Nasked Kanae-san's forgiveness,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.79,0:38:56.07,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,not even once.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.56,0:39:00.13,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,I have no intention of lessening the \Ncompensation for a person like you. {Double-checked against Ep 1 -E}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.29,0:39:04.43,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Ichikawa-san. You truly \Nare in pain, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.89,0:39:05.55,Bengoshi-Flashback,Ichikawa,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.04,0:39:06.93,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.22,0:39:10.74,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,it is only proper we \Ndemand compensation. {Checked against ep 4}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.70,0:39:25.45,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Ambulance,Manga bubble pan to bottom; bubble1,0,0,0,,You're nothing but a third-rate\N ambulance chaser!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.24,0:39:25.45,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Ambulance,Bubble2,0,0,0,,{\a10\3c&H364A54&}I have representation by a first-rate law firm, you're in for a treat!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.36,0:39:25.03,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,Can you stand living \Nwith him as you have,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.77,0:39:28.20,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,for the next 25 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.20,0:39:29.18,Bengoshi-Flashback,Fumiko,0,0,0,,I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.53,0:39:30.69,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,In that case,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.25,0:39:32.73,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,all we can do is forge ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.40,0:39:36.23,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,The total membership fees \Nand compensation...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.09,0:39:38.12,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,you will pay, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.64,0:39:41.38,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,After all, you shallowly judge \Npeople based on appearances...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.05,0:39:44.70,Bengoshi-Flashback,H,0,0,0,,you're not qualified to \Noversee human encounters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.57,0:39:53.85,Bengoshi-Manga_Bubble_Ambulance,Lower manga bubble,0,0,0,,{\fad(1960,0)\3c&H35505E&\b1}I never turn anyone down\N if they are truly in need.{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.37,0:39:58.20,Bengoshi-Flashback,K,0,0,0,,You have always put yourself \Nin your clients' shoes, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.20,0:40:00.76,Bengoshi-Flashback,K,0,0,0,,Then you'd always find the \Nbest ways to help them.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.92,0:40:02.85,Bengoshi-Flashback,K,0,0,0,,Because he doesn't stand a chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.85,0:40:04.52,Bengoshi-Flashback,K,0,0,0,,Those aren't Hakamada-sensei's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.28,0:40:24.34,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I'm glad you came, Hakamada-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.09,0:40:26.21,Default,H,0,0,0,,Thank you for yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.73,0:40:28.36,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,Since you're here,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.36,0:40:30.00,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,I assume you're accepting my offer?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.89,0:40:31.65,Default,H,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.93,0:40:33.53,Default,H,0,0,0,,With regard to the offer,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.53,0:40:35.29,Default,H,0,0,0,,I respectfully decline.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.05,0:40:36.82,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.75,0:40:39.86,Default,H,0,0,0,,I came here today because there \Nis something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.65,0:40:43.73,Default,Keiko,0,0,0,,And what could that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.05,0:40:50.60,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,First of all, please give me 1,200 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.81,0:40:51.46,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.00,0:40:54.38,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,That's the charge for the \Nglass of wine you drank.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.76,0:40:59.25,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,It's fine to put on airs \Nand walk out of the bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.77,0:41:03.63,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,but you should pay for \Nyour own beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.63,0:41:06.31,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,Still as petty as ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.96,0:41:14.96,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,And I believe we will be suing \Nyour client, Honjo Yayoi-san's husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.96,0:41:18.92,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,Honjo Takashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.63,0:41:21.02,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,Are you joking?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.81,0:41:23.63,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,You don't stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.81,0:41:25.94,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,A lawyer who turns down clients
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.28,0:41:27.82,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,because he believes he \Ndoesn't stand a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.82,0:41:29.67,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,is not a lawyer in my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.14,0:41:35.05,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,I know I'm overstepping \Nmy bounds, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.77,0:41:40.41,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,you should be prepared to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.62,0:41:46.63,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,Your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.50,0:41:56.90,Bengoshi-Final_Episode,Caption,0,0,0,,The shocking final episode
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.90,0:42:05.57,Bengoshi-Next_Episode,,0,0,0,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.10,0:41:58.59,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,I am prepared \Nfor disbarment.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.59,0:42:00.45,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,Now that it's gone to court,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.97,0:42:02.07,Bengoshi-End_Splash1,Caption,0,0,0,,{\c&H6C41FB&}The final battle, {\c}laying his life as an attorney on the line
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.45,0:42:01.88,Bengoshi-Top,Keiko,0,0,0,,there's no way you can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.88,0:42:03.63,Bengoshi-Top,Kur,0,0,0,,Damn, she got us good.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.10,0:42:05.67,Bengoshi-End_Splash2,Caption,0,0,0,,What will be Hakamada Yukio's{\c&H19CDB8&} fate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.63,0:42:06.08,Bengoshi-Top,K,0,0,0,,I won't take\N this lying down.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.74,0:42:09.44,Bengoshi-Fiction,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,0)}This drama is a work of fiction
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.08,0:42:08.82,Bengoshi-Top,H,0,0,0,,Now, let me make a counterargument.

